          <strong>61, Male</strong>
        </div>
        Retired
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="one-third column">
      <img class="benefits-icon" src="/static/img/pitcher.svg">
      <h3>Run Self Experiments</h3>
      <div class="testimonials-item">
        <p>
          After years of vomitting when having the slightest amount of alcohol, I found out that the type of the birth-control pill I was taking was the cause! I just switched to a different brand and now I can have a drink without any side effects.
        </p>
        <img src="/static/img/user_f.svg">
        <div>
          <strong>26, Female</strong>
        </div>
        Waitress
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="one-third column">
      <img class="benefits-icon" src="/static/img/goal.svg">
      <h3>Monitor Life Goals</h3>
      <div class="testimonials-item">
        <p>
          I decided to lose some weight and get in shape, so I started monitoring my weight, workouts and nutrition. It's nice to see a chart with an overview of my progress, keeps me motivated.
        </p>
        <img src="/static/img/user_m.svg">
        <div>
          <strong>31, Male</strong>
        </div>
        IT Manager
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row hidden">
    <div class="one-third column">
      <img class="benefits-icon" src="/static/img/note.svg">
      <h3>Keep a Daily Journal</h3>
      <div class="testimonials-item">
        <p>
          I made a habit of writing my thoughts and experiences every day, and it has truly changed my life. It keeps me focused on my goals, reduces scatter in my life, and helps me recognize what needs to be removed and what should be included in my life. Couldn't recommend it enough!
        </p>
        <img src="/static/img/user_m.svg">
        <div>
          <strong>31, Female</strong>
        </div>
        Writer
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="one-third column">
      <img class="benefits-icon" src="/static/img/treasure.svg">
      <h3>Record Your Life History</h3>
      <div class="testimonials-item">
        <p>
          I like the idea of re-experiencing my past with todayâ€™s mind. Once in a while I go over my old stuff and recall happy, sad and funny moments I had with old friends.
        </p>
        <img src="/static/img/user_f.svg">
        <div>
          <strong>39, Female</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="one-third column">
      <img class="benefits-icon" src="/static/img/plus.svg">
      <h3>Add Yours!</h3>
      <div class="testimonials-item editable">
        <p>
          <textarea id="testimonials-form-text" rows="4"></textarea>
        </p>
        <div class="display-flex">
          <img src="/static/img/user_m.svg">
          <input id="testimonials-form-age" type="number" placeholder="Age">
        </div>
        <input type="text" id="testimonials-form-description" placeholder="Who are you?">
        <div class="flex-center">
          <button>Submit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="testimonials-toggle" class="text-center">
    <button class="show-more">
      <img src="/static/img/chevron-arrow-down.svg">
      Show more
    </button>
    <button class="show-less">
      <img src="/static/img/chevron-arrow-up.svg">
      Show less
    </button>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="marketing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="two-thirds column">
        <h2>Tracking Health Symptoms</h2>
        <p>
          Record your medications, diet and any factor you can think of that influence how you feel. Find out what keeps your symptoms under control.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="one-third column">
        <img class="marketing-icon" src="/static/img/tablets.svg">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
document.getElementById('testimonials-toggle').addEventListener('click', function() {
  document.getElementById('testimonials').classList.toggle('open');
});
</script>

